{"tid":1799764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老師錯愛非洲窮男 三年生八小孩","createTime":"2019-12-27T07:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T14:51:43.000Z","uid":209657,"like":47,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"29d4ceac76a2b49df012be652bc91ad7b6d9933f","tid":1799764,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"內地一名女老師小何經歷婚姻失敗後，一直不敢輕易投入愛情，直至她認識一名非洲裔男子後，毅然決然放棄原來生活，和對方遠赴非洲結婚定居，三年內生了八個小孩，原來是其丈夫的「陰謀」。<br />\n<br />\n小何不但外型亮眼，薪水亦相當高，月入約1.7萬港元，但因為曾離婚，小何遲遲不敢再相信愛情，直到她認識一名非洲裔男子，覺得自己找到真愛，決定放手一搏，遠嫁他鄉。<br />\n<br />\n嫁到非洲後，小何短短三年內懷孕多次，每次都是多胞胎，共生了八個孩子，原來是因為夫家的家境貧困，生小孩能夠領政府大筆的育兒補助金，才一直逼她生小孩。<br />\n<br />\n小何感十分後悔，奉勸女生千萬不要因為一時的衝動，失去理智，「看清楚你想要的生活」。"},{"pid":"9cace33137f0e22dc4349f3a865560e5cbf4ee61","tid":1799764,"uid":99642,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"O"},{"pid":"e68cd3c4ee661ccb541dce10de5fb7affaef45ec","tid":1799764,"uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191227/_2019122708201468354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191227%2F_2019122708201468354.jpg&h=fb22f807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1668072/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E9%8C%AF%E6%84%9B%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%AA%AE%E7%94%B7-%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%9F%E5%85%AB%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A9%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%94%9E%E8%A3%9C%E5%8A%A9%E9%87%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1668072%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E9%258C%25AF%25E6%2584%259B%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E8%25A2%